Death rates for Scotland

Source: R/hmd_data.R
hmd_data_scot.Rd

Data from the Human Mortality Database on the 1x1 age and period central death rates (mx) for the Scotland population. Death rates are stratified by sex only. Ages 16-89 selected

Usage

hmd_data_scot

Format

A data table.

Source

Human Mortality Database - Scotland
